      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look and fall in love!",
