    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking showroom condition, this vehicle is a genuine time capsule for the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, completely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, complemented by pristine alloy wheels and factory-fresh trim. Inside, the cabin remains untouched; the premium leather is supple with absolutely no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a documented full service history and a drive that is as tight, quiet, and responsive as the day it was delivered. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with precision. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved masterpiece that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open checkbook.",
